ter font-bold rounded-xl transition-all active:scale-[0.98] disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none gap-2.5 cursor-pointer no-underline tracking-tight bg-transparent text-zinc-500 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-[11px] px-4 py-1.5 uppercase tracking-widest h-8 text-[10px]\">Example</button></div></div><div class=\"lg:hidden\"><div class=\"flex p-1 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-xl \"><button class=\"\n              flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-lg transition-all flex-1\n              bg-white text-black shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]\n            \">Edit</button><button class=\"\n              flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-lg transition-all flex-1\n              text-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-200 hover:bg-white/[0.02]\n            \">Preview</button></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 min-h-[600px]\"><div class=\"block flex flex-col space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-1\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white/20 uppercase tracking-widest\">Markdown Source</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-accent uppercase\">91<!-- --> Words</span></div><textarea placeholder=\"Start writing...\" class=\"flex-1 w-full p-6 rounded-3xl bg-[#0d0d0d] border border-white/10 text-white font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent/50 resize-none custom-scrollbar\" spellCheck=\"false\"># Markdown Professional Editor\n\nExperience real-time GFM preview with industrial-grade styling.\n\n## ✨ Features\n- **Live Preview**: See your changes as you type.\n- **GFM Support**: Tables, task lists, and more.\n- **Quick Toolbar**: One-click formatting.\n\n## 🛠️ Tech Stack\n```ts\nimport { marked } from &#x27;marked&#x27;;\nconst html = marked.parse(markdown);\n```\n\n| Feature | Status |\n| :--- | :--- |\n| Speed | Fast |\n| Privacy | 100% Client-side |\n| Styling | Tailwind CSS |\n\n&gt; &quot;The best way to predict the future is to create it.&quot;\n</textarea></div><div class=\"hidden lg:block flex flex-col space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-1\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-white/20 uppercase tracking-widest\">Live Rendering</span><button class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white/40 hover:text-white uppercase transition-colors\">Copy HTML</button></div><div class=\"flex-1 rounded-3xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 p-8 overflow-auto custom-scrollbar prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none\"><div><h1>Markdown Professional Editor</h1>\n<p>Experience real-time GFM preview with industrial-grade styling.</p>\n<h2>✨ Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Live Preview</strong>: See your changes as you type.</li>\n<li><strong>GFM Support</strong>: Tables, task lists, and more.</li>\n<li><strong>Quick Toolbar</strong>: One-click formatting.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>🛠️ Tech Stack</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-ts\">import { marked } from &#39;marked&#39;;\nconst html = marked.parse(markdown);\n</code></pre>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Feature</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Status</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"left\">Speed</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Fast</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">Privacy</td>\n<td align=\"left\">100% Client-side</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">Styling</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Tailwind CSS</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<blockquote>\n<p>&quot;The best way to predict the future is to create it.&quot;</p>\n</blockquote>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h4 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-accent tracking-[0.2em]\">Privacy</h4><p class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">Processing happens strictly on your machine. No data is ever transmitted or stored.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h4 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white tracking-[0.2em]\">Open Source</h4><p class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">Verified by the community. Part of the WokSpec Global Open Source Protocol.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h4 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white tracking-[0.2em]\">Performance</h4><p class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">Optimized for sub-millisecond response times using browser-native APIs.</p></div></footer></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script>$RB=[];$RV=function(a){$RT=performance.now();for(var b=0;b<a.length;b+=2){var c=a[b],e=a[b+1];null!==e.parentNode&&e.parentNode.removeChild(e);var f=c.parentNode;if(f){var g=c.previousSibling,h=0;do{if(c&&8===c.nodeType){var d=c.data;if(\"/$\"===d||\"/&\"===d)if(0===h)break;else h--;else\"$\"!==d&&\"$?\"!==d&&\"$~\"!==d&&\"$!\"!==d&&\"&\"!==d||h++}d=c.nextSibling;f.removeChild(c);c=d}while(c);for(;e.firstChild;)f.insertBefore(e.firstChild,c);g.data=\"$\";g._reactRetry&&requestAnimationFrame(g._reactRetry)}}a.length=0};\n$RC=function(a,b){if(b=document.getElementById(b))(a=document.getElementById(a))?(a.previousSibling.data=\"$~\",$RB.push(a,b),2===$RB.length&&(\"number\"!==typeof $RT?requestAnimationFrame($RV.bind(null,$RB)):(a=performance.now(),setTimeout($RV.bind(null,$RB),2300>a&&2E3<a?2300-a:$RT+300-a)))):b.parentNode.removeChild(b)};$RC(\"B:0\",\"S:0\")</script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[21935,[\\\"2619\\\",\\\"static/chunks/2619-04bc32f026a0d946.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-25dcb334fddea283.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[9766,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[98924,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[52619,[\\\"2619\\\",\\\"static/chunks/2619-04bc32f026a0d946.js\\\",\\\"4345\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/not-found-e74fab4940a99c10.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[17900,[\\\"